Doc Del,<br>
     If you want to go toe to toe with others on Vietnam &amp; any related topics, enjoy!  However, I wouldn't put my go-round wuth Jeffrey down as &quot;fun&quot;.  Personally, I'd rather be hit by a truck.  Having your parents' veracity denigrated is not my idea of a good time.  When he said that it was just &quot;bad men&quot; that shadowed our home; all I could think of was the cartoon character &quot;Baby Tooth&quot; shouting his trademark: &quot;BAD MANS!&quot;.  He'll lay down a fact or sensible statement on one line; then go off on a tangent that seems to belon to an alternate reality.  Hope you, tanker and wingman fare better.  As for me engaging Jeffrey any further; I'm waiting for an apology.  I wouldn't be true to my Mom and dad otherwise.<br>
                                   Gerry
